<h2 data-section-id="67yn9l" data-start="470" data-end="488">3. Exportar CSV</h2>
<p data-start="490" data-end="551">En <code data-start="493" data-end="513">app/admin/page.tsx</code>, dentro de <code data-start="525" data-end="534">Admin()</code>, justo antes de:</p>
